Package com.google.api.client.util

Added Classes and Interfaces
BackOff Back-off policy when retrying an operation.
BackOffUtils Beta
Utilities for BackOff.
Beta Use this annotation to indicate that a public API (class, method or field) is beta.
ExponentialBackOff Implementation of BackOff that increases the back off period for each retry attempt using a randomization function that grows exponentially.
ExponentialBackOff.Builder Builder for ExponentialBackOff.
Sleeper Sleeper interface to use for requesting the current thread to sleep as specified in Thread.sleep(long).
